Class Stock

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tectonica.jonix.onix3.Stock
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OnixComposite, OnixComposite.OnixSuperComposite, Serializable

    public class Stock
extends Object
implements OnixComposite.OnixSuperComposite, Serializable

    Stock quantity composite

    A repeatable group of data elements which together specify a quantity of stock and, where a supplier has more than one warehouse, a supplier location. Optional.

    Reference name <Stock>
    Short tag <stock>
    Cardinality 0…n
